metadata.name: Keith Haring's Photo Collage By R.V. (Robin Van Aristol)
metadata.description:
Keith Haring's Photo Collage By R.V. (Robin Van Aristol) -  
This collage relating to Keith Haring was made shortly after the exhibition "Keith Haring And The New York City Street Artists" at La Posteria in Milan, Italy 1997. R.V was the Co-curator of this exhibition with Paulo Buggiani and has documentation and photographs of Keiths work. There are also several photographs on the collage from Keith's exhibition at Tony Shafrazi gallery in the early 1980â€™s
